{
  "stem": "16473.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was there in front of me, and it was, it was horrible.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The net result of that was that I never wanted to find out about what happened in concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was afraid to read about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't want to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean as an adult, it was just [SIGHS] [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I-- I don't know what to say.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was just a terrible experience.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was terrible for the people that it happened to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was terrible to show it to a child that young.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was terrible to-- for me as a child to have realized that I could have been one of those people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[SOBBING] And it was just an overwhelming experience, I guess.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] When-- when I tried to get some kind of spiritual support or leadership from my parents, I didn't get it because my dad didn't have it in his background.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I think my mother out of her rebellion, there was just nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I had a severe need for something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I remember going out on a balcony and praying, looking up at the stars and praying.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't know if I stood or I knelt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I know I was looking for something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And maybe it was to try to put all this together, [SOBBING] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But because I didn't get it from my parents, I started quizzing our cleaning ladies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, they told me about Jesus, and I was very interested in hearing the stories.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was very adept and I'd go to school and I'd say to the Catholic kids, have you heard this story yet?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'd be like ahead of them, because my interest was just so intense and so propelling.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
